title: SST for Brexit
instruction_to_fill: Mark Low, Medium, High or Not Sure for Potential Threats against Impact on the business if Brexit happens, Probability of this happening (affecting my industry), Level of confidence that the business is prepared to exploit an opportunity or can deal with
scoring_guidelines: Don't Know' button represents answers that genuinely reflect ignorance or lack of knowledge. The Combined Factor Score is Impact * Probability * Confidence
